<% if calculator.due_date >= Date.parse("2026-04-05") && calculator.due_date <= Date.parse("2026-07-25") %>
  ##Paternity leave

  The mother’s partner can take up to 2 weeks' [paternity leave](/paternity-pay-leave/leave).

  Paternity leave must be used by <%= format_date(calculator.take_paternity_leave_by_date) %>.

  From 18 February 2026 until 25 July 2026, the partner does not need to give the usual 15 weeks notice of their baby’s due date.

  The partner must still tell their employer when they want their leave to start - by <%= format_date(calculator.give_paternity_leave_notice_by_date) %>

<% else %>
  The parents cannot get maternity leave or pay or paternity leave or pay.
<% end %>
